Package no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data

Class Accounting

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1002.app.data.Accounting
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Bookkeeping
public class Accounting extends Object implements Bookkeeping, Serializable
The Accounting class represents a bookkeeping system for tracking income and expenses for the accounting of a project. It implements the Bookkeeping interface and is Serializable for serialization and deserialization.
